{"tid":465582,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支港人「天貓課金」全球排第二   最愛買連衣裙衛衣","createTime":"2017-11-11T16:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-12T16:00:14.000Z","uid":79563,"like":27,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"2ef7f42c7705b22015ba97894331764821f04579","tid":465582,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510406940_0ab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171111%2Flarge%2F1510406940_0ab5.jpg&h=8163f464&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n截至今晚九點，天貓「雙11」成交額又創新高，除了支那客消費力強勁，亦有賴支港人積極「課金」，因為在貨物出口國家或地區排名中（支那以外），香港位列第二，僅次俄羅斯，台灣暫為第四。<br />\n<br />\n數據顯示，支港人特別鍾情服裝類產品，最受歡迎產品排名首三位分別是連衣裙、針織衫及衛衣；而澳門及台灣則愛電子類產品，分別鍾愛廚房電器及數碼相機。此外，支港人於「雙11」消費力強勁，按年節節上升，反而澳門及台灣今年「雙11」消費則稍有回落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171111/57447434\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57447434&d=f5WNX%2Bhpoj89CKswZk6Y30%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2BLvdN%2BZCE%3D&h=8e7ffc49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171111%2F57447434&h=376964b3\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20171111/57447434</a>"},{"pid":"2759b659a7c988c8828da33eb330adafefe3ea94","tid":465582,"uid":50740,"like":27,"dislike":10,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"屌你老母!係都要俾支那人賺"},{"pid":"d8e61fadd93b07445c355d770f313a82e26d8a69","tid":465582,"uid":145277,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-11T16:32:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171111/large/1510406940_0ab5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F201711